videos.description: Trailing for most of the game, Florida State takes the lead in the fourth quarter when Deondre Francois hits Travis Rudolph for the 19 yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Francois hits Rudolph to put Seminoles up late

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Francois hits Rudolph for late TD) 2016/11/05 ESHEET

videos.description: Breaking down Florida State's 24-20 win over NC State
videos.headline: Breaking down Florida State's 24-20 win over NC State

videos.description: No. 22 Florida State overcomes a 10-point deficit in the third quarter, eventually taking the lead on a 19-yard touchdown catch by Travis Rudolph, to beat NC State 24-20.
videos.headline: Florida State comes back to top NC State
